name: Legs
description:
Size: 8"x12"

Printed by a professional lab on Lustre Kodak ENDURA professional photo paper with a fine grain pebble texture. It literally will last a lifetime. Not like a cheap inkjet print.

This photograph was taken with a 35mm film camera and film usually produces grain. Colors may look different from what you see on your monitor. And at certain photos there is cropping.

All prints are shipped in between two pieces of cardboard. I ship USPS first class within 2-3 business days for USA and for international please allow 7-14 days.

No refunds, unless it is due to a shipping damage. In that case I will need the damage photo before I ship a new one.
